Day 15 – Astrology & Life Analysis using Claude

Objective

Explore how AI can generate a detailed Vedic Astrology and Life Analysis report using structured prompts and organize the results into meaningful sections.

---

Tools Used

- Claude AI
- GitHub

---

Prompt Used

Used a detailed Vedic Astrology & Life Analysis prompt based on:

- Parashara Astrology
- Jaimini Astrology
- Nakshatra Analysis
- Vimshottari Dasha
- Transit Analysis

The prompt requested:

- Birth Chart Summary
- Life Pattern Analysis
- Career & Wealth Analysis
- Relationship & Marriage Analysis
- Current Dasha Analysis
- Five-Year Forecast
- Remedies and Recommendations

---

Personal Inputs Provided

- Full Name: [Your Name]
- Gender: [Your Gender]
- Date of Birth: [DD/MM/YYYY]
- Birth Time Accuracy: [Exact/Approximate/Unknown]
- Place of Birth: [Your Birth Place]
- Current City: [Your Current City]
- Relationship Status: [Single/Married/etc.]
- Profession: [Student/Professional]
- Top Three Current Concerns:
  1. Career Growth
  2. Financial Stability
  3. Personal Relationships

---

Sections Generated by Claude

1. Birth Chart Summary

The report included:

- Lagna (Ascendant)
- Moon Sign
- Sun Sign
- Nakshatra and Pada
- Planetary Placements
- Major Yogas and Doshas
- Functional Benefic and Malefic Planets

---

2. Life Pattern Analysis

Analysis covered:

- Core personality traits
- Childhood and family influences
- Repeating life patterns
- Relationship tendencies
- Career strengths and weaknesses
- Financial habits and challenges

---

3. Career & Wealth Analysis

The report examined:

- Career suitability
- Job versus business inclination
- Leadership potential
- Government job possibilities
- Foreign opportunities
- Wealth accumulation potential
- Property and investment prospects

Age ranges for:

- Career breakthroughs
- Wealth growth periods
- Challenging phases

were also discussed.

